---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Method"
  description="Track & Tote publishing method for source checks, attribution, caveats, and readable interpretation."
>
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="kicker">Method</p>
    <h1>How we keep it clear and lawful</h1>
    <p>Each article is published only after source, license, and claim-scope checks.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="method-grid">
    <article>
      <h2>1. Question first</h2>
      <p>Start with a focused public question before selecting a chart.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h2>2. Source checks</h2>
      <p>Confirm license, attribution terms, update cadence, and known data gaps.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h2>3. Match scale</h2>
      <p>Align geography and timeframe before comparing variables.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h2>4. Publish caveats</h2>
      <p>State what the evidence can show and what it cannot prove.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
